window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Changing history, one disaster at a time....</p> <p>Itâ€™s been a year since Sam traveled back to the past, and his mission is far from over.</p> <p>With mermaids being kidnapped and the dwarven civil war heating up, Sam is the best hope for saving his world from total destruction.</p> <p>Armed with knowledge of the future, Sam must use every advantage he has to get stronger and more powerful with each passing day.</p> <p>Will Sam be able to gain enough power to alter history once again?</p> <p><i>Second Chance Swordsman 2 </i>continues the best-selling LitRPG/Progression Fantasy series by Jakob Tanner, author of <i>Tower Climber</i> and <i>Arcane Kingdom Online</i>. The story contains RPG mechanics, stats, and ranks as a form of power progression.</p>"; 
